UPDATE public.processes
	SET  
       status='Success',
       "timestamp"='${now():format("yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss.SSS\'Z\'")}'    
    WHERE 
       transactionId = '${id}';

UPDATE public.processes
	SET  
       status='Error',
       "timestamp"='${now():format("yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss.SSS\'Z\'")}'    
    WHERE 
       transactionId = '${id}';
